name: Chained Escape
summary:
🍕The long-awaited Public Lobby is finally here!
Meet up with other penguins, play basketball, or even start a food fight!
This is your new social hub to hang out, show off your cosmetics, and find teammates to escape with.
Whether you're chilling between runs or here to conquer the stages, the Public Lobby is the place to be! 🏀

⛓️ Linked by Chains, Bound by Fate ⛓️
"Chained Escape" is an immersive VR game where players control penguins chained together, striving to reach the summit. Supporting...
